title: Wall Street Ngegas di Tahun Baru, Dow Jones Rekor
description: Bursa saham Amerika Serikat (AS), Wall Street, menutup hari dengan manis. Semua indeks utama mengalami kenaikan, dalam penutupan perdagangan, Senin (3/1/2021).
keywords: wall street, bursa as, amerika serikat

title: Wall Street abre o ano em alta com recordes do Dow Jones e SP500
description: A bolsa nova-iorquina acabou hoje em alta, com novos recordes dos índices seletivo Dow Jones Industrial Average e alargado S&P500, graças a uma recuperação do otimismo dos investidores.

title: Next logical step for Apple is the metaverse - Loup Ventures' Gene Munster (NASDAQ:AAPL)
description: With Apple (AAPL) touching the $3T level in market cap, Loup Ventures analyst Gene Munster said the metaverse represents the next logical step for the iconic iPhone maker.
